Wideband demo image: ubr10k2-k9p6-mz.2005-01-05.DEMO_FINAL_BUILD


Wideband configuration CLI:

- Preconfiguration for Modena
    # card 3/0/0 24rfchannel-vpa-1

- Controller configuration
    (config)# controller wideband-cable 3/0/0
    (config-controller)# annex B modulation 256qam 0 23
    (config-controller)# ip-address 192.168.200.6 mac-address aaaa.bbbb.cccc
    (config-controller)# wideband-host subslot 7/0

- RF channel configuration
    (config-controller)# rf-channel 0 frequency 770000000

- Associate RF channel to wideband channel
    (config-controller)# rf-channel 0 wideband-channel 0 pid 49152
                                    bandwidth-percent 100


--------------------------------------------------------------------

How to poke memory on UBR10k:

- Use CLI: test crash
- Select C to enable crashing
- Select U to write an address with 0x11111111


